  <brief_title>Prospective Multicenter Registry On Radiation Dose Estimates Of Cardiac CT Angiography in Daily Practice in 2017 (PROTECTION VI)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prospective Multicenter Registry On Radiation Dose Estimates of Cardiac CT Angiography in Daily Practice in 2017 (PROTECTIONVI)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
